@list(unordered) {
    @item () {
        something
    }
}

single newline is a soft break
and this line stays in the same paragraph.

blank line starts a new paragraph.

backslash newline is a hard break\
so this line starts after a hard break.

inline macro hard break happens here@br
and this line follows the macro break.

